            "created": "20150710115738986",
            "creator": "TonGerner",
            "text": "A plugin for a top menu and a switchable left menu.

The tiddler [[Top menu|$:/plugins/tg/topleftmenu/topmenu]] need to be populated with tag based top menu entries.

The tiddler [[Left menu|$:/plugins/tg/topleftmenu/leftmenu/entries]] need to be populated with menu entries (based on links, tags, tagpills, sliders, TOC macro, ...).

For more information see ''Left + top menu'' guide at: http://www.tongerner.nl/TW5/TW5_playground.html

<<<
''Note:''<br>''This plugin needs my [[$:/plugins/tg/layout]] plugin for general layout settings (available at http://www.tongerner.nl/TW5/TW5_playground.html).''
<<<

Settings for the layout can be found in ''~ControlPanel > Appearance > [[Plugin tweaks|$:/plugins/tg/layout/tweaks]]''.
